  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To develop a cohort of COPD participants to assist study staff in determining the most likely
      candidates for future studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To develop a cohort of COPD participants for study staff to determine the most likely
      candidates for future studies and to develop a repository of blood from subjects with COPD
      for future studies.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
